   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Give the Gift of Joy this Christmas</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will give essential supplies to help support a girl in rural Tanzania to complete her education in safety and comfort. Since 2012 Lyra has built 11 hostels, housing over 1,000 girls per year.   Our Christmas appeal aims to give small gifts directly to the girls in Lyra hostels, helping to make their learning and living environment more comfortable, and to extend the learning equipment they have available. We need your help to give them the much-needed gift of Joy this Christmas.</narrative>
  </description>
